originalSql:
SELECT 
    n.n_name AS nation_name,
    COUNT(DISTINCT s.s_suppkey) AS supplier_count,
    SUM(CASE WHEN p.p_size > 10 THEN ps.ps_availqty ELSE 0 END) AS large_part_avail_qty,
    AVG(p.p_retailprice) AS avg_retail_price,
    STRING_AGG(DISTINCT p.p_name, ', ') AS part_names,
    MAX(o.o_totalprice) AS max_order_total_price
FROM 
    supplier s
JOIN 
    nation n ON s.s_nationkey = n.n_nationkey
JOIN 
    partsupp ps ON s.s_suppkey = ps.ps_suppkey
JOIN 
    part p ON ps.ps_partkey = p.p_partkey
LEFT JOIN 
    lineitem l ON ps.ps_partkey = l.l_partkey
LEFT JOIN 
    orders o ON l.l_orderkey = o.o_orderkey
WHERE 
    n.n_name LIKE 'N%'
GROUP BY 
    n.n_name
HAVING 
    COUNT(DISTINCT s.s_suppkey) > 5
ORDER BY 
    nation_name

SELECT COALESCE("t5"."NATION_NAME", "t5"."NATION_NAME") AS "NATION_NAME", "t5"."SUPPLIER_COUNT", "t5"."LARGE_PART_AVAIL_QTY", "t5"."AVG_RETAIL_PRICE", "t5"."PART_NAMES", "t5"."MAX_ORDER_TOTAL_PRICE"
FROM (SELECT MIN("nation"."n_name") AS "NATION_NAME", COUNT(DISTINCT "supplier"."s_suppkey") AS "SUPPLIER_COUNT", SUM(CASE WHEN "part"."p_size" > 10 THEN "partsupp"."ps_availqty" ELSE 0 END) AS "LARGE_PART_AVAIL_QTY", AVG("part"."p_retailprice") AS "AVG_RETAIL_PRICE", LISTAGG(DISTINCT "part"."p_name", ', ') AS "PART_NAMES", MAX("s1"."o_totalprice") AS "MAX_ORDER_TOTAL_PRICE"
FROM "supplier"
INNER JOIN "nation" ON "supplier"."s_nationkey" = "nation"."n_nationkey"
INNER JOIN "partsupp" ON "supplier"."s_suppkey" = "partsupp"."ps_suppkey"
INNER JOIN "part" ON "partsupp"."ps_partkey" = "part"."p_partkey"
LEFT JOIN "lineitem" ON "partsupp"."ps_partkey" = "lineitem"."l_partkey"
LEFT JOIN "s1" ON "lineitem"."l_orderkey" = "s1"."o_orderkey"
WHERE "nation"."n_name" LIKE 'N%'
GROUP BY "nation"."n_name"
HAVING COUNT(DISTINCT "supplier"."s_suppkey") > 5
ORDER BY 1) AS "t5"
